|Example.Text=سیاست پدر و مادر ندارد.
|Example.Gloss=Politics does not have parent.
|Example.English translation=Politics has no roots or genealogy 
|Example.Comments=Having parents implies a sense of genealogy and roots, people who do not know their parents are looked down upon as people with "no history," no roots. This metaphor implies that politics acts/is . like a person with no loyalty to family and follows his/her own agenda--Aria F
 
